1:09:59 Colorized version of Shock / El susto, Choc, Schock!, 惊吓疗法, Choque!

Summary:

A psychologically distraught woman is locked away in a private sanitarium, haunted by a violent memory she can’t fully recall. As her mind slowly unravels the truth, she finds herself in a deadly cat-and-mouse game with her own psychiatrist—a man with far more sinister plans than healing. Trapped in a web of deceit and danger, she must outsmart her captors before they make her their next victim. In a place where no one can be trusted, her fight for survival becomes a pulse-pounding race against time.

Main Cast:

Vincent Price as  Dr. Richard Cross
Lynn Bari as Nurse Elaine Jordan
Frank Latimore as Lt. Paul Stewart
Anabel Shaw as Mrs. Janet Stewart
Stephen (Michael) Dunne as Dr. Stevens
Reed Hadley as District Attorney O'Neill

This film is available with English, German & Spanish audio, and subtitles in many languages.
